/server/interact/3791/', '[1] Myers MG, Iazzetta JJ "Intranasally administered phenylephrine and blood pressure." Can Med Assoc J 127 (1982): 365-6[2] Cass E, Kadar D, Stein HA "Hazards of phenylephrine topical medication in persons taking propranolol." Can Med Assoc J 120 (1979): 1261-2', 1767369485);
